I '''John Hadji Argyris''' ([[Greek alphabet|Greek]]: Ιωάννης Αργύρης; * [[Agostu 19]] [[1913]] i king Volos, [[Greece]]; – [[Abril 2]] [[2004]] king [[Stuttgart]]) iya ing metung kareng linalang keng [[Finite Element Method]] (FEM) at dati [[Professor]] king [[University ning Stuttgart]] ampong Director na ning Institute para Statics ampong Dynamics na ning Aerospace Structures. <br />
Ing kayang bapa [[Constantin Carathéodory]] metung yang Greek [[mathematician]] na ning [[Makabayung Panaun]].

== Scientific a obra ==
I Argyris kasangkut ya keng pamanalkus ning Finite Element Method kambe nang [[Ray W. Clough]] ampong [[Olgierd Zienkiewicz]] kaibat ning maranun a mathematical minunang obra nang [[Richard Courant]].

